snippet.title: Sonicomi Gameplay Preview Trailer
snippet.description:
See more details at http://sonicomi.com
Take the role as Super Sonico's private cameraman, leading her on the  path to fame. You'll need to select the best outfits and locations so she can impress each client. Your direction and success will shape Sonico's future modeling career. Will she become a sexy cosplayer or an international super model? She is willing to do anything with you as her cameraman!
